lettercontent:
Hello! I am a For X from China. I am very happy to write to you!
To be frank, I never imagined that I would one day become a star follower, let alone fall in love with Kpop. After all, I could be described as a conservative person before I fell in love with you. I basically only listen to Chinese classical music. I like classical poetry, and rarely touch anything avant-garde.
But your appearance proves that, when you like a person, all the principles can be broken for him. I started playing your songs on loop. I fell in love with your dancing. I also began to try things I had never done before, and recieved a brand-new version of myself.
You have such magic that I'm convinced you will be a hit. Come on, For X will love you forever!

lettercontent:
Hello, Yechanni! I am your Chinese fan. I wonder if you can see this letter?
 By coincidence, I went to watch your TV drama and was deeply hooked on you at once, and  then started to follow stars for the first time in my 20-year life.
Before knowing you, my life was muddled. Although I never seemed to encounter any major setbacks, and even was admired by others because of the admission to a top university, I still felt that I was incomplete and often fell into a sense of nothingness. And you and OX came along to fill that void. When I started to follow you, I began to feel that I was genuinely 'alive'.
It feels hypocritical to say this, but it's from my heart. I will be there for you all the way!

lettercontent:
I know you have been very tired lately, with an invisible sense of physical and mental exhaustion, but please persevere.
Even if no one is interested or your skills are inferior, don't let worry and anxiety ruin your already limited enthusiasm and determination.
Don't be greedy, we can't have everything. Don't worry, we can't have nothing either.

lettercontent: The scenery of life will not always be sunny and sunny. Perhaps the rain will continue tomorrow, or the lightning and thunder will be right now. Don't doubt the beauty of everything because of temporary difficulties. Please firmly believe that a beautiful future belongs to you! As long as you put aside your troubles and move forward courageously, your life will be sunny every day!

lettercontent:
For ForX's favorite OXs!
      
       I am a Chinese fan! Also a new fan! I got to know everyone and gained an understanding of their past through the 
TV drama of JaeHan and YeChan.
       
       Everyone has embarked on a new journey, and China's ForX will always support OX! Those who pursue their dreams are always the best!
       
       How are everyone doing lately? The beautiful and green spring is about to pass! Is everyone's return to the stage also coming! I miss your so much!                     
       
        Thinking of going over and over again to paint the stage, I have almost finished watching everyone's previous stage! We believe that everything is improving and there will be more ForX by everyone's side!                   
      
       We have also heard about the recent events in South Korea and have a heartfelt message to share with everyone:
       
        Please have regular physical  examinations and eat well.
        If feeling unwell, please rest well.
        Please put yourself first.
        Please maintain a happy mindset.
        Please believe in yourself, Please believe ForX.
        Please do not commit to being arrested by the police.
        Welcoming the warm sunshine of spring and waiting for the warmth of summer .

        looking back at the past of OX, we ForX look forward to opening upï¼

               
                  Always support your Chinese fans

lettercontent: Hello. I am a fan from Shaanxi, China. I know you must know China, but Shaanxi may not be known to you, but it doesn't matter. Just remember that I am your Chinese fan and there are many people who love you in China. Although you may not see this letter, I still want to write to you. From the first time I saw you to now, I thought you were a very cold person from the beginning, but now I think you are cute and responsible. It didn't take a long time, I don't know why, but I have always vaguely felt that you are a very easy to get along with. After getting to know you, sometimes I will see your responsible side, and sometimes I will see you and your members acting coquettishly. The ever-changing nature of you makes me feel that you are a person worth being loved, I hope you and your members can be healthy and happy every day in the future. Please remember me, I will always be behind you. As long as you turn your head, you can see me. Don't worry about me walking away. I will always be there and support you. Fighting!

lettercontent:
To OMEGA X
       I don't know if you'll read this letter I wrote, but I did, and maybe you'll see it. First of all, I am sorry, I am not very good at Korean, English is not good, afraid you think Chinese is not easy to understand the use of the machine flip.
        I have a lot to say to you, but when I start writing, I don't know what to write. You are the first Korean regiment I chased. Before I met you, I never thought I would like a regiment so much, because as far away as China, all your messages I received were much slower, resulting in a lot of activities I couldn't take part in, but every time I saw you standing on the stage in the video, I felt that everyone was shining, and it would make me feel like I was on the scene. How I wish I could meet you, even if I really just saw a back, well, that's it for emotional words.
         I have a hunch that OMEGA X will be hot, but after the fire, you should also pay attention to the body oh, do not work too hard, I just hope that each of you is healthy, happy, love you

lettercontent:
Dear Jaehan,
       I am a little fan from China. For me,you are the only star I love deeply,and this is my first time to write a letter to the people I love.Please remember you deserve everyone's love! I like OX,but of all the eleven members in OX,you are my favorite.Your voice make me peace and happiness,your personality make me deeply fascinated. I sincerely hope you can always be a lovely boy without sorrow and anxiety,always do what you like and enjoy the process of singing and dancing.I really really want to see you are healthy and happy.
        If you are ready,then you come, I'm looking forward to see you again in big stage. But if you are not ready, that's okay,I'll be there for you all the way and support you forever!
       Take good care of yourselves!Love you forever !OX fighting!

Dear jaehan, Hello, this is my first letter to you. I am very happy because a TV play made me know you. I really like when you laugh. You won't think I like you because of your teeth.           A letter from For X in China. In fact, I also wrote a letter to 11 of you yesterday. Hahahaha

lettercontent:
Dear OX members:
        Although I am just a little fan from China,but you know,in China, you already have a lot of fans.You all are definitely excellent idols, don't doubt yourselves,be confident!We are very glad to be your fans and fall in love with you all. Because of you,we gain a lot of happiness,but also fell sorry and angry about what you went through. Fortunately,you've already dealt with it,and we're so excited that you're finally free! So We wish you just be happy. If you are ready,then you come,we are looking forward to see you again in big stage. But if you are not ready, that's okay,we'll be there for you all the way and support you forever!
      For me,you are the only group I love deeply,and this is my first time to write a letter to the people I love.Please remember you deserve everyone's love!
       ê¹€ì¬í•œ ,my dear Kim Jae Han,you are my favorite in OX,your voice make me peace and happiness,your personality make me deeply fascinated. I sincerely hope you can always be a lovely boy without sorrow and anxiety,always do what you like all the time and enjoy the process of singing and dancing.I really really want to see you are healthy and happy.
       Take good care of yourselves!Love you forever!OX fighting!

lettercontent:
Hi,I'm a fan from China and I'm glad to have the opportunity to write to youã€‚First of all, thank you for being there so that I can love you. I regret that I didn't meet you sooner and didn't give you more support, it must have been hard along the way, right? lettercontent:
TO:OMEGA X

       Hello, I am Forx from China. When I learned that I could write to you, I was really happy to tell you how much I like you. I'm sorry to meet you so late, but I will accompany you down the road in the future. I think you are the best in my eyes. I really like your songs and I also like all of you. I am particularly moved by the fact that you have been through such things and have been united in your journey. There is a saying in China: 'How can you see a rainbow without experiencing wind and rain?'. I will always be with you. Let's take the flower road together. Always love you. Come on, the best OMEGA X. When else can you come to China for a tour?     
                                             China forx   Y

Hello, I am a fan from China. At first, I liked jeahan and yechan. Because of the TV drama 'Comfort the Young'. But as my understanding of you deepens, I love all of you. I like the tiger teeth of jeahan, the angel faces of yechan and yanghyeok, Kevin's cuteness, the fox eyes of jehyeon,junghoon  who can dance well, our pistachios taedong and sebin, and I also like the cool and cute myeongiu and Xen. Your songs have been on my playlist these past few days. I watch your videos and variety show repeatedly. Through these, I have found that you all have great talent and are very gentle and sincere towards your fans. Although I cannot go to Korea to see you now, I can support you through the screen. Many people in China like you. I hope you can eat and sleep well, take care of yourself, and not get sick. You are great, and I will always support you. Finally, I hope you are happy every day, and I hope you can take the path of flowers. I love you all. (Mobile translation may have errors, I hope you can understand)

lettercontent:
Dear omega x, I am a fan from China and I am very happy to express my love to you in this way. But please forgive me, I am learning Korean, and I may not be able to express my meaning well through the translator. I'm sorry to meet you so late, but I believe that we can accompany each other for a long time. Thanks to the two members of the show, let me realize that you are shining in the place I have not been to, and thank you for holding on till now, hold on until we meet. I look forward to you hanging in there with me until I become a better person and really come to you and meet you!
To be honest, before watching the TV series, I was going through a very confused period in my life. I was also very decadent and didn't know where I should go. But thank you very much, Omega x brings me countless strength, as long as listening to your songs, I feel every day is full of energy! We are all looking forward to your songs, and I hope that our 11 brothers can get back to the fans, and I hope that you can get back on your feet! There are more Chinese fans than you think. I can assure you that new days and new hopes are encouraging us to keep moving forward. You will always be the direction of my efforts, which is always the reason why I love you!
Jeahan, you are the captain of the team, and you have been leading Omega x for a long time. You are also my favorite person. I hope I can become as excellent as you, and your singing always encourages me to become a better person! Thank you for coming into my world! Hwichan, happy birthday to you! I also watched your birthday live, you are really a very lovely and beautiful person, if you stand in front of me, with your charming eyes looking at me to talk, no matter what I will agree! Your singing is very unique, also very charming, everyone likes you very much! Sebin, your perfect face is exactly my ideal type. In the variety show, your composure fascinates everyone. I hope you can continue to shine on the stage! Hangyeom, your rap really impressed me when I got to know Omega x. Originally, I thought you were a very indifferent boy, but I didn't expect you to be a very cheerful boy. I hope you can always be so happy when we move forward together in the future. Taedong, when you were a member of 202, I was in junior high school. At that time, I was fascinated by your dance shape of you. In the school performance, I stood in your place and performed the dance again in front of my classmates. Thank you for reappearing in my life! Xen, first of all, thank you very much for sending photos in Chinese on Instagram, which made countless Chinese fans feel our response. We are really very happy and love your sincerity. We are moved by you. Your tattoo is really sexy, I hope it doesn't cover up next time! Anyone who covers your tattoos or rejects them, I think they have no taste! You are so charming on stage! Jehyun, the first time I saw your eyes, I thought I was enchanted, because they are really beautiful eyes, like a fox. You also sing like an elf, attracting a lot of fans. Kevin, really, you are so cute! Although I am younger than you, I think if I had a son like you, I would be the happiest mother in the world! I hope you can always be so lovely, so happy! As the pettish representative of our Omega x! Junghoon, as the leader of our dance, you really did a great job! You make every dance very distinctive. I am also a dance lover and am learning Omega x's dance. I hope I can dance as well as you one day! You are my best dance teacher! Hyuk, with your lovely face and charming body, I thought you were a senior high school student when I first met you, because you look just like my senior in the university. Keeping exercise is the first condition of health! Get fit and stay healthy with Omega x! Yechan, my most lovely baby, your composure is beyond my expectation. As the youngest brother, you have more experience to deal with more things than your peers. Thank you for your wonderful performance in the TV series. Of course, I still think you're cute! Cute is more than handsome!
Omega x, Chinese fans are looking forward to your new album! Our wallets are ready! Music charts may be a little difficult for us, but sales can certainly be better with our charge! Please believe that there are still a lot of fans in China who like you. Please also take a look at our Chinese fans.
From a Chinese fan who loves you -- Coral Snake

Dearï¼ŒJaehan.
    I am your Chinese fans, I am glad  you played a shoulder to cry on, I met you through this show. You are really attractive. I can't believe how someone can be so cute and sexy. In that show, you showed us your super high acting skills and really had chemistry with yechan.
    Your TV drama is really hot in China, and now there are more fans who are happy for you, we gather together FOR X to help you vote, in order to let you stand on the big stage.
     Jaehan, I will always be with you, FOR Xare also, continue to do their own, we like this kind of you, Chinese fans heard of your former company did those things, really chilling, we are very sad, but the final termination of the contract, we can also recognize the new OMEGA X. All right, let's not talk about these sad things. You just need our Chinese fans to like you very much. If you have the opportunity to speak more Chinese in the future, we will be very happy.
    Jaehan, I would like to mention a small wish. Can you do more business with Ye Chan? Really like the sense of atmosphere you have together. Hope you will always be together and both put each other first. Love you both.
    Love you forever.

Only then did I know what a good group of pups I had missed. Now that I am a graduate student, I began to vote frantically and watch the views again. Thanks to you, I had a lot of first time experiences. Thank you very much for making me feel like I am young again. How can you have a group that sings and dances well, that's good-looking and that works hard and that arranges and choreographs and writes lyrics? How dare the company do that to you! lettercontent:
Hello everyone from OMEGA X! I am FOR X. from China. I am delighted to have this opportunity to express my joy and love for meeting you in this way. The pursuit of beauty is human nature (serious facekkkkk), and I admit that at the beginning, I started to pay attention to it because of your good looks. Later, I saw your debut group variety show and was immediately amazed by your talent! And then I fell hopelessly in love with you!I am fortunate to have met you all, and your attitude towards setbacks has greatly touched and encouraged me! Thank you very much for giving me the opportunity to continue liking you, whether it's your choice to make a second debut and pursue your dreams again, or your willingness to appear in front of us even after being greatly hurt this time recently. Thank you very much!Because of OMEGA X, I realized the meaning of "chasing stars": you who bravely and persistently pursue your dreams with all your might, shining on the stage like stars breaking through the darkness to illuminate my life, making me feel the passion and expectation of living. Let me want to pursue you, to pursue the world that you have made me see that is more worth longing for!Perhaps we are still in a stage that is not ideal, but please do not give up no matter what. Please continue to work hard! We, FOR X, will always be with you. I believe we will definitely take the path of flowers together!Jaehanã€Hwichanã€Sebinã€Hangyeomã€Taedongã€Xenã€Jehyunã€Kevinã€Junghoon ã€Hyuk and Yechan LOVE YOU!

I'm really confused now, but after I met you, I seem to be I found the direction and saw you acting, singing and dancing on the stage. I really admire you. You can also write lyrics and compose music, and many musical instruments. I like them very much, but I won't. I want to learn more from you, learn more knowledge, and make myself strong. Give you encouragement! I hope you are getting better and better, happy and healthy. Please encourage me! Let's work together! I hope I can work with you one day! Love you!

lettercontent:
Jaehan, I am a fan from China! Please A shoulder to cry onthrough this drama to recognize you and Ye chan. Then met OMEGA X, the next letter will be very long, whether you can see I want to tell you this feeling.
When I first met you, I thought you were very cute and lively. I always thought you were a younger brother, but I didn't expect you to be the eldest brother on the team. I am always happy to look at your lovely smile. I was sick when I first met you. Thank you for the joy you brought me during that time. After watching please comfort the young man, I also seemed to be comforted by the slaughter, and the disease gradually recovered.
Then, I went to see the previous video only to find that you have suffered so many bad things, I am very sad to see such a cheerful and lively jaehan experienced such injustice. Jae han ah, you really hard, a person to bear a lot of it should be very tired. But I also want to thank you for your persistence, thank you for standing on the stage with OMEGA X, standing in front of us, thank you for not giving up on that kind of thing. Thank you for always being so gentle, responsible and strong. I really love this Jae han, even in a foreign country, I will always support Jae han!
Many, many fans in China are liking you! If only you knew, we will try our best to vote for you and we will support you when you return! Thank you and Ye chan for being in this drama. Because Jae han and Ye chan, now I'm in love with eleven very nice people! I love you, Jaehan. ğŸ’š I LOVE OMEGA X! â¤ï¸
Ps: I'm really sorry if there's something wrong! I will try to learn Korean!

After watching your stadium activities a few days ago, everyone looked good. Although I can't see you, you have added a lot of happiness to my life. I hope to see you on the stage next time. I'm sorry for starting to like you so late. If I can, I will go with you in the future. More and more China fans like you, so we should all cheer together. lettercontent: When I happened to see the A Shoulder To Cryry On, I realized that the two characters' experiences were similar to mine, and that they were happy people, but I couldn't trust others completely, express my true feelings directly, and unconsciously refused and ignored them.I got to know you through the drama, and later I got to know OMEGA X. Coincidentally, we found out that it was similar to our experiences, and that we had a new beginning at the same time and experienced the hardest things, but now we have a new beginning.Nice to meet you and OMEGA X. Let me have the courage to start a new life. Let's walk on the flower path together.I will always support you and OMEGA X, and I hope that whoever I like will be able to become better physically and bring you good luck

I think people with beliefs and dreams will never lose. Come on!

lettercontent: Hi Yechan, I am For X from Taiwan. Although I am not sure if you will see this letter, I still want to write down some words that I want to say to you. Your birthday is only ten days apart from mine, so you are my oppa! Haha. I first heard of your name during "Under Nineteen" and 1THE9. I remember you were a child with many camera shots, but I didn't pick you at that time, and I am really sorry. I had the impression that you seemed a bit distant, which is not my favorite type, but now I really love you!!! After watching () I realized that you are a treasure, and I went back to watch the audition program again. Not only can you sing and dance, but you also help other younger brothers in private. You are really an excellent Yechan. Although you are not the main vocalist in Omega X, you are very capable of rapping. You are really talented, and I was so moved!!! I really like Yechan's singing voice. It gives people a comforting feeling. Now when I listen to Omega X's songs, I always look for your voice. I hope to hear more of Yechan's voice in the future.
